*Adder.py*
 - has all the GATES/Logical Circuits as classes
 - has the 8 bit Ripple Carry Adder logic

*Utilities.py*
 - has all the bit conversion utility functions

*main.py*
 - Main function through which the program runs

*testAdder.py*
 - run this module to test if the accuracy of the logic is correct
 - generates random number in a range and then checks the accuracy



To run the main program : 
main #: python3 main.py

To test the code : 
test #:python3 testAdder.py

Compatibility : Python3.4 and above
